most of the time don't like it, don't share it,

29
0:01:35.515,000 --> 0:01:37,000
don't nothing,

30
0:01:37.738,000 --> 0:01:38,000
and it's another day.

31
0:01:39.731,000 --> 0:01:42,000
So I went to sleep, and that was it for me.

32
0:01:43.683,000 --> 0:01:45,000
And later on in the night, I woke up

33
0:01:46.599,000 --> 0:01:47,000
because I'm always waking up in the night,

34
0:01:48.432,000 --> 0:01:5,000
and I went by the computer and I see all these red dots,

35
0:01:51.007,000 --> 0:01:54,000
you know, on Facebook, which I've never seen before.

36
0:01:54.159,000 --> 0:01:55,000
(Laughter)

37
0:01:55.242,000 --> 0:01:57,000
And I was like, "What's going on?"

38
0:01:57.579,000 --> 0:02:,000
So I come to the computer and I start looking on,

39
0:02:01.083,000 --> 0:02:04,000
