53
0:02:45.867,000 --> 0:02:46,000
So I'm like, whoa.

54
0:02:47.549,000 --> 0:02:5,000
I ask my wife to come, and I tell her, you have to see that.

55
0:02:50.967,000 --> 0:02:53,000
